data.description: Immaculate well cared for contemporary home located in Hempfield Township !! A spacious bright and airy inviting open floor plan best describes this home. A large fenced in private backyard with two sheds and a  cute playhouse and play set is perfect for the kids and a pet. This  home also has both a screened in patio with cable TV hookup and a deck off the back perfect for lazy summer evenings with the family and friends. Updated kitchen with an  island  and newer counter tops.  Master bedroom with walk in closet and full bath !  The finished lower level is an entertainers dream equipped with a  bathroom and bar setup with a granite  counter top.  Mounted TV stays with the sale of the home. Concrete drive and sidewalk. Landscaped front yard. Quiet neighborhood !!.. Key less entry on garage door. Extra storage room off the back of  the garage . Security system in place..  Most  appliances .. Best yet the kids catch the bus right at the end of the driveway .
